-I'M -- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

37:07.225 --> 37:08.601
-IN YOU GO.

37:08.643 --> 37:10.062
LOCK IT.

37:10.103 --> 37:12.022
WELL, THAT'LL HOLD HER

37:10.103 --> 37:12.022
