37:22.199 --> 37:25.160
SHE SET YOU UP AS A SCAPEGOAT.

37:27.162 --> 37:29.122
FELICIA WAS SHAVING POINTS,

37:29.164 --> 37:31.083
YOU KNOW, FIGURING

37:29.164 --> 37:31.083
NO ONE WOULD NOTICE,

37:31.124 --> 37:32.876
'CAUSE YOU WERE CALLING

37:31.124 --> 37:32.876
BAD PLAYS,

37:32.918 --> 37:36.004
