SO -- SO THE COACH

37:36.046 --> 37:37.380
WOULD TAKE THE BLAME

37:37.422 --> 37:38.631
-IF SOMEBODY WENT LOOKING.

37:37.422 --> 37:38.631
-THERE YOU GO.

