-YEAH, YEAH, YEAH.

37:38.673 --> 37:40.800
-OH, MY GOD.

37:40.842 --> 37:42.969
OH, MY G-- I LET THIS HAPPEN.

37:43.011 --> 37:46.598
I'M LIKE T-THE JOE PISARCIK

37:43.011 --> 37:46.598
OF GREETING-CARD EXECS,

37:46.639 --> 37:47.849
DROPPING THE BALL

37:47.891 --> 37:49.601
SO HERM EDWARDS

37:47.891 --> 37:49.601
CAN RUN IT BACK FOR THE WIN.

37:49.642 --> 37:51.561
"MIRACLE AT THE MEADOWLANDS."

37:51.603 --> 37:54.522
GIANTS AND EAGLES IN, UH, '78 --

37:54.564 --> 37:55.941
RALLIED THE EAGLES

37:54.564 --> 37:55.941
TO THE PLAYOFFS.

37:55.982 --> 37:57.234
HELL OF A PLAY.

37:57.275 --> 37:58.944
-ARE YOU A GRIDIRON MAN?

37:57.275 --> 37:58.944
-LIFELONG.

37:58.985 --> 38:01.696
BEEN WATCHING GAMES WITH MY POP

37:58.985 --> 38:01.696
SINCE I WAS 2.

38:01.738 --> 38:04.157
AH, WELL, IF THAT'S THE CASE,

38:01.738 --> 38:04.157
YOU'RE GONNA REALLY LIKE

38:04.199 --> 38:07.244
THE, UH, THE NEW CARD LINE

38:04.199 --> 38:07.244
HE'S WORKING ON.

