38:10.329 --> 38:13.917
"REMEMBER,

38:10.329 --> 38:13.917
WHEN IT'S CRUNCH TIME...

38:15.543 --> 38:18.379
...YOU CAN ALWAYS CALL

38:15.543 --> 38:18.379
MY NUMBER, DAD."

38:18.421 --> 38:22.801
NOW, THAT'S HOW MEN,

38:18.421 --> 38:22.801
REAL MEN, EMOTE.

