38:31.184 --> 38:34.146
NO, THE  CHAMPIONSHIP.

38:42.320 --> 38:43.571
OKAY?

38:43.613 --> 38:45.991
SO, WHAT DO YOU THINK?

38:46.032 --> 38:48.618
I THINK IT'S TERRIFIC.

38:48.660 --> 38:50.203
ABSOLUTELY UPLIFTING.

38:50.245 --> 38:51.997
HEARTWARMING, EVEN.

38:50.245 --> 38:51.997
DON'T YOU THINK?

38:52.038 --> 38:54.124
YEAH, IT WAS A STORY

38:52.038 --> 38:54.124
