38:58.003 --> 38:59.296
-IT'S SO HOPEFUL.

38:58.003 --> 38:59.296
-HOPEFUL.

38:59.337 --> 39:01.464
YEAH. YOU KNOW, YOU COULD

38:59.337 --> 39:01.464
SELL THIS TO HOLLYWOOD.

