HOLLYWOOD?  NEIN!

39:03.049 --> 39:04.884
THAT IS NOT THE POINT!

39:04.926 --> 39:08.513
THE POINT IS TO EXPOSE

39:04.926 --> 39:08.513
THE FUTILITY OF LIFE...

39:08.554 --> 39:09.848
OH, IT DOESN'T DO THAT.

39:09.889 --> 39:12.184
...THE EVER-PRESENCE OF DECAY,

39:12.225 --> 39:17.314
NOT TO PEDDLE SIMPLISTIC,

39:12.225 --> 39:17.314
NARRATIVE PABLUM!

39:17.355 --> 39:18.315
IT IS NOT.

